          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Get Regulation Out of the Way Act of 2015 or the GROW Act of 2015 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002 to exempt from the auditor attestation of internal control assessments an issuer of securities whose total market capitalization is less than $2 billion.</p>]]></text>
